The files in this repository are used to control per-VM firewall rules
when running GENICloud as a vanilla PlanetLab installation.

NodeManager/gc_iptables.py
--------------------------
PlanetLab NodeManager plugin for generating a GENICloud node's
iptables configuration. 

MyPLC/globalinfo.py
-------------------
Testbed-wide information used by the gc_iptables plugin.

MyPLC/slices.py
---------------
Used by the gc_iptables plugin.  For each GENICloud slice, lists the
source IP addresses or networks from which SSH to VMs is permitted. 
